channel.title: [SOLVED]Help with richscape client
channel.description:
Figured it out i had to change all the 50L's to 49L's
Whenever i try compiling the client i get this: [code]Applet_Sub1.java:5: cannot access sign.signlink bad class file: .\sign\signlink.class class file has wrong version 50.0, should be 49.0 Please remove or make sure it appears in the correct subdirectory of the classpa th. import sign.signlink; ^ 1 error Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
